platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Hamster wheels for exercise? Fishing ponds filled with capybaras? There’s so much cuteness packed into this idle resort game—we may never leave!
倉鼠輪可以鍛鍊身體？釣魚池裡都是水豚？這款放置式度假遊戲非常可愛，讓人愛不釋手！
Hamster wheels for exercise? Fishing ponds filled with capybaras? There’s so much cuteness packed into this idle resort game – we may never leave!
Hamster wheels for exercise? Fishing ponds filled with capybaras? There’s so much cuteness packed into this idle resort game–we may never leave!
在這款可愛無極限的放置型休閒遊戲裡，你可以布置倉鼠滾輪，在滿是水豚的池塘裡釣魚，打造屬於你的夢幻天地。
Des roues de hamster pour faire du sport, des points d’eau visités par des capybaras, il n’y a pas plus mignon que ce jeu incrémental. On ne s’en lassera jamais !
